yingyinNormal.en: I'm a CDO manager. A CDO manager? Yeah, at Harding Advisors.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是个债务担保经理。债务担保经理？在哈丁顾问公司工作。

yingyinNormal.en: I went in there, and the general manager. And assistant general manager were like, "we gotta let you go. We're trying to get Deandre Jordan."
yingyinNormal.zh: 我走到楼上，然后总经理和助理总经理说，“我们得裁掉你，我们想要德安德鲁乔丹”

yingyinNormal.en: I am not his campaign manager. You think he has a chance?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不是他的竞选经理。你觉得他行吗？

yingyinNormal.en: I spoke to her and her manager who confirmed with CCTV that she was on a shift. Checks out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我和她以及她的经理谈过话了经理看过监控确认了她当时在上班。不在场证明对得上。

yingyinNormal.en: What's this? I want you to be my general manager. That's my offer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是什么？我想邀你来当经理，这是我开的条件。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, yeah, right. I invited your campaign manager over so you can meet him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对了，我邀请了你的竞选经理来，你们能见个面。

yingyinNormal.en: As most of you know, today I am proud to be naming a new regional sales manager.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家都知道，今天我要宣布新的区域销售经理。

yingyinNormal.en: Who's it up to, Bob? My manager, Nelson Olstead. I only do what he says.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谁说了算，鲍勃？我的经理，尼尔森·奥斯特德，他说什么我做什么。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, and some thanks I got. The assistant manager chased me out with an artisanal salami.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是啊，但他们都不感激，助理经理还用手工制意大利香肠赶我走呢。

yingyinNormal.en: It's my manager again. She's always on me. Can't wait till the fall when she's off to college.
yingyinNormal.zh: 又是我经理，她总是盯着我，等不及到秋天她去上大学的时候了。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm flattered you would do this on my account, but being manager isn't worth killing Mr. Krabs over.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很感谢你为我做这些，但是没当成经理还不至于要杀了他啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Miss Jones? I am Mr. Safir, the hotel manager. I trust your flight was pleasant? Like a magic carpet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 琼斯女士吗？我是萨菲尔，酒店经理。航班还满意吗？就像张魔毯。

yingyinNormal.en: This is why I told the manager I wouldn't wait on you tonight. Oh come on. Don't be such a baby.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那就是为什么我告诉经理我不想为你服务的原因。少来了，别那么幼稚。

yingyinNormal.en: Mrs. Svorski. I have someone who I think can be the perfect manager for when I can't be at the bakery.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斯沃斯基太太，我想到一个人绝对是我不在时担任面包房经理的最佳人选。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, I've had to learn how to balance being a friend and a manager. You could call it being a Franager.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也是慢慢学着如何在做朋友和做经理之间保持平衡，你可以称之为做"朋理"。

yingyinNormal.en: This went back and forth a couple of times, so she is blurted out in frustration, my manager is bad. That he understood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 经过几轮之后，她只好说了一句很简单的话 "我的经理很糟糕"。他终于懂了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《Facebook COO谢丽尔·桑德伯格哈佛演讲》

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm hearing that Peter truly is running for president and that I might be First Lady from his campaign manager.
yingyinNormal.zh: 皮特真的要竞选总统，以及我可能成为第一夫人，这件事是他的竞选经理告诉我的。

yingyinNormal.en: And this is A.P.Y. Collections? Yes. Bob Bondi. But I already complained to his manager and he won't do anything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是APY追讨公司的人？是的，鲍勃·邦迪，我已经跟他的经理投诉过了，但他不肯有所作为。

yingyinNormal.en: Because today is the grand opening ceremony for The Krusty Krab 2, where Mr. Krabs will announce the new manager.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为今天就是克鲁斯 克莱伯餐馆二号的开幕仪式！仪式上，克莱伯先生将会宣布新的经理的名字。

yingyinNormal.en: The modern feedlot business is really an extension of the corn business. Explaining the connection is facility manager Mike Thoren.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现代的饲养产业是玉米产业的一个延伸。正在向我们解说的是工厂的经理，麦克·瑟伦。
